image_analysis.description: A financial disclosure form, specifically OGE Form 278e, for Donald J. Trump. The page, A21 of 47, details ownership structures for various business entities, listing the entity name, who owns it, the percentage of ownership, and their role. The document is a black and white scan with some highlighted fields.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a header with form details and filer's name. The main body is structured into sections, each identified by a reference number and an entity name. Each section contains fields for 'Owned by' and 'Has ownership interest in', with columns for percentage, name, entity name, ownership, title, and role. A footer contains a document identifier.
